Title: Freak the Freak Out (1)
Plot: Jade and Cat participate in a karaoke singing competition at Karaoke Dokie with Hayley Ferguson and her friend Terra, and even though the crowd enjoyed Jade and Cat's song more, Hayley won because her dad owned the karaoke place. Meanwhile, Tori is stuck at home taking care of Trina, who is in massive pain due to her wisdom teeth being removed. Angry that Hayley and Terra cheated, Jade makes up a scheme involving Tori.
